snippet.title: Wild Terra 2: New Lands. Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Play your role in the life-filled medieval world controlled by players. Live on an inhabited territory or conquer New Continents in new seasons! In-development MMORPG, full of logically interconnected worked out little things that create a unique immersion and adventure.

The game will be created with the financial support of our community. Become a part of a joint dream and history! 
Pledge and Alpha access: https://www.wildterra2.com/
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1134700/Wild_Terra_2_New_Lands/
Music by misharoot: https://vk.com/misharoot
